Package: archives.gov
Title: National Archives (NARA) Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for National Archives open datasets and
    Catalog API. Proposed Constitutional amendments (1787-2014), NHPRC grants,
    Nixon White House Tapes, and Catalog search (requires API key).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
